## About
This platform provides a complete solution for a cleaning services company, including:

- Public-facing website for customers (no login required)
- Customer portal (optional login)
- Employee portal (login required)
- Admin portal (login required)
- Super Admin portal (login required)
- Online booking and payments
- Role-based access control, reporting, and audit logs
- Integration with Stripe, Twilio, and Google Maps

## Features

### Customer Website (Public)
- Home, Services, Service Pages, Pricing, Booking, Reviews, FAQs, About, Contact, Careers, Blog, Policies
- Online booking & Stripe payments (no login required)
- Service catalog: Home, Office, Specialty cleaning

### Customer Portal (Optional Login)
- Dashboard, Appointments, Cleaning Status, Saved Addresses, Invoices & Payments, Ratings & Reviews, Messaging, Profile

### Employee Portal (Login)
- Role-based access: Digital Marketing, Cleaners, Record-Keeping, Floater
- Dashboard, Todayâ€™s Jobs, Geo Clock In/Out, Job Checklists, Photos, Timesheets, PTO Requests, Incident Reporting, Training Center, Performance KPIs

### Admin Portal (Login)
- Scheduling & Dispatch, Customer Management, Employee Management, Job Management, Billing & Invoices, Payroll, Inventory Tracking, Reports & KPIs, Messaging, Notifications, Issue Resolution

### Super Admin Portal (Login)
- Admin User Management, System Settings, Pricing Matrix, Service Catalog Editor, Branding Manager, Integrations, Financial Reports, Audit Logs, Security Permissions

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend:** React / Next.js
- **Backend:** Node.js / Express
- **Database:** PostgreSQL
- **File Storage:** AWS S3
- **Authentication:** JWT, Secure Password Hashing, RBAC, Admin & Super Admin 2FA
- **Integrations:** Stripe, Twilio, Google Maps
- **Other:** HTTPS, Mobile-responsive UI

